Title: Appropriate Uses For SQLite

Title: Digital Driver’s Licenses Could Become a Real Option in Some States
Description: Several states have run pilots for digital driver’s licenses, which would allow residents to supplement plastic ID cards with smartphone apps. But as the technology becomes more of a reality, experts are worried about the privacy implications.
